msgstr "Tell me about Jewel itself."

msgctxt "1164_Employee"
msgid "Jewel is a hostess club with a  laid-back atmosphere and friendly, down-to-earth girls."
msgstr "Jewel is a hostess club with a  laid-back atmosphere and friendly, down-to-earth girls."

msgctxt "1176_Employee"
msgid "It's my top recommendation! You can find it over on Shichifuku Street."
msgstr "It's my top recommendation! You can find it over on Shichifuku Street."

msgctxt "1188_Employee"
msgid "There's an 8,400 yen cover charge, a 3,150 yen hostess-selection charge, and a 3,150 yen service charge."
msgstr "There's an 8,400 yen cover charge, a 3,150 yen hostess-selection charge, and a 3,150 yen service charge."

msgctxt "1212_Employee"
msgid "Tell me about Noa Mizutani."
msgstr "Háblame de Noa Mizutani."

msgctxt "1224_Employee"
msgid "Noa-chan is cheerful and friendly. Talking to her is like talking to a good friend, even if you've only just met."
msgstr "Noa-chan is cheerful and friendly. Talking to her is like talking to a good friend, even if you've only just met."

msgctxt "1236_Employee"
msgid "She's a little ditzy at times, but I think you'll find it charming－especially when she doesn't realize she's being ditzy!"
msgstr "She's a little ditzy at times, but I think you'll find it charming－especially when she doesn't realize she's being ditzy!"

msgctxt "1248_Employee"
msgid "She's 21, an Aquarius, and her blood type's B! She loves to eat anything fried but hates bitter vegetables."
msgstr "She's 21, an Aquarius, and her blood type's B! She loves to eat anything fried but hates bitter vegetables."

msgctxt "1260_Talk_Smile"
msgid "Hehehe... Once you get a taste of Noa-chan's cheery personality, you won't be able to stop coming back for more!"
msgstr "Jejeje... Una vez que pruebes la alegre personalidad de Noa-chan, ¡no podrás dejar de volver a por más!"

msgctxt "1284_Employee"
msgid "Tell me about Erena Aihara."
msgstr "Tell me about Erena Aihara."

msgctxt "1296_Employee"
msgid "Erena-chan is a spunky Kansai goddess! Her high energy is absolutely infectious."
msgstr "Erena-chan is a spunky Kansai goddess! Her high energy is absolutely infectious."

msgctxt "1308_Employee"
msgid "Here's something you might not expect: she also has a girly side! Your heart is guaranteed to skip a beat once you get a glimpse of it!"
msgstr "Here's something you might not expect: she also has a girly side! Your heart is guaranteed to skip a beat once you get a glimpse of it!"

msgctxt "1320_Employee"
msgid "She's 24, an Aries, and her blood type's O! Her favorite food is liver sashimi, and I hear she's really into perfume."
msgstr "She's 24, an Aries, and her blood type's O! Her favorite food is liver sashimi, and I hear she's really into perfume."

msgctxt "1332_Talk_Smile"
msgid "Hehe... Let me tell you, once you live through one of Erena-chan's hyper-energetic conversations, you'll be totally hooked!"
msgstr "Hehe... Let me tell you, once you live through one of Erena-chan's hyper-energetic conversations, you'll be totally hooked!"

msgctxt "1356_Employee"
msgid "Tell me about Chihiro Ikki."
msgstr "Háblame acerca de Chihiro Ikki."

msgctxt "1368_Employee"
msgid "Chihiro-chan's a college student! She's popular for her exceedingly normal personality－at least, normal compared to most hostesses."
msgstr "¡Chihiro-chan es una estudiante universitaria! Es popular por tener una personalidad excesivamente normal - \"normal\" en comparación con la mayoría de las demás hostesses."

msgctxt "1380_Employee"
msgid "You can tell she's trying really hard to keep up with \"adulting,\" as she'd call it. You'll want to watch over her and protect her!"
msgstr "You can tell she's trying really hard to keep up with \"adulting,\" as she'd call it. You'll want to watch over her and protect her!"

msgctxt "1392_Employee"
msgid "Just between you and me, I hear she's hiding a secret talent... Wonder what it could be."
msgstr "Just between you and me, I hear she's hiding a secret talent... Wonder what it could be."

msgctxt "1404_Employee"
msgid "She's 20, an Aries, and her blood type's B! I hear she's not very good with alcohol, despite working in a hostess club."
msgstr "She's 20, an Aries, and her blood type's B! I hear she's not very good with alcohol, despite working in a hostess club."

msgctxt "1416_Talk_Smile"
msgid "Hehehe... You'd best be careful with Chihiro-chan. One innocent look is all it takes for an addiction to start!"
msgstr "Je, je, je... Será mejor que tenga cuidado con Chihiro-chan. ¡Una pequeña e inocente mirada es suficiente para volverte adicto!"

msgctxt "1440_Employee"
msgid "Tell me about Maya Mori."
msgstr "Tell me about Maya Mori."

msgctxt "1452_Employee"
msgid "Maya-chan is cool and stylish. She has a mysterious kind of charm about her, though maybe that comes from how calm and refined she comes off as."
msgstr "Maya-chan is cool and stylish. She has a mysterious kind of charm about her, though maybe that comes from how calm and refined she comes off as."

msgctxt "1464_Employee"
msgid "She loves going out on the town at night and has plenty of stories to tell about her nighttime adventures, though lately I hear she's grown up a little bit."
msgstr "She loves going out on the town at night and has plenty of stories to tell about her nighttime adventures, though lately I hear she's grown up a little bit."

msgctxt "1476_Employee"
msgid "She's 24, a Sagittarius, and her blood type's A! She absolutely loves chocolate, don't forget that."
msgstr "She's 24, a Sagittarius, and her blood type's A! She absolutely loves chocolate, don't forget that."

msgctxt "1488_Talk_Smile"
msgid "Hehehe... Just you wait. You'll take one look at Maya-chan's cute face and instantly fall in love!"
msgstr "Hehehe... Just you wait. You'll take one look at Maya-chan's cute face and instantly fall in love!"

