msgstr "I hear there are even customers who come up all the way from Kansai just to meet Himeka-chan!"

msgctxt "1788_Employee"
msgid "She's 24, a Leo, and her blood type's O! She loves liver sashimi and fried foods, and I hear she's really into collecting perfume and going to hot springs."
